OL,3,C'Nowhere to go': Charities facing
OL,4,Ceviction by council from the community
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FA charity facing eviction from the
OL,8,Fcouncil has condemned the selling of
OL,9,Fthe community centre and fears they
OL,10,Fwill have "nowhere else to go".
OL,12,FAmanda Ball, who is the scheme co-
OL,13,Fordinator of charity Shopmobility, has
OL,14,Fsaid Leicestershire County Council
OL,15,Fwrote to all the occupants of the
OL,16,Fcentre on 4 April telling them they
OL,17,Fwere selling Roman Way Community
OL,18,FCentre and that they'd have to leave.
