OL,3,C'Nowhere to go': Charities facing
OL,4,Ceviction by council from the community
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FThis decision could leave many of its
OL,8,Ftenants, including community services
OL,9,Fand charities, without a home.
OL,11,FShopmobility, who provide mobility
OL,12,Fscooters and wheelchairs, is one of
OL,13,Fthe charities based in the centre.
OL,15,FAmong those facing eviction are Home
OL,16,FFarm Trust, a learning disability
OL,17,Fsupport service, and I Care meals on
OL,18,Fwheels. They've been given an extended
OL,19,Fdeadline of 31 October to leave.
