OL,3,C'Nowhere to go': Charities facing
OL,4,Ceviction by council from the community
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FShopmobility has said they haven't
OL,8,Fbeen able to find anywhere else to go.
OL,9,FThey need lots of storage space to
OL,10,Fhouse there 30 mobility scooters and
OL,11,Fwheelchairs along with their workshop.
OL,13,FA regular customer, Sandra Clegg,
OL,14,Fsaid: "It's not just about having a
OL,15,Fplace to rent scooters near to town,
OL,16,Fshopmobility stores a wide range of
OL,17,Fmobility aids and also has a workshop
OL,18,Fto repair equipment."
