OL,3,C'Nowhere to go': Charities facing
OL,4,Ceviction by council from the community
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FA community interest company is
OL,8,Flooking to purchase the community
OL,9,Fcentre, and they are happy for
OL,10,FShopmobility to stay. But it is not
OL,11,Fguaranteed their bid will be
OL,12,Fsuccessful.
OL,14,FMarket Harborough District Council
OL,15,Fhave said: "Roman Way Community Centre
OL,16,Fin Market Harborough has been
OL,17,Fregistered as an Asset of Community
OL,18,FValue following an application
OL,19,Fsubmitted to the council by a
OL,20,Fnominating group.
