OL,3,C'Nowhere to go': Charities facing
OL,4,Ceviction by council from the community
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"If a property is listed as an Asset
OL,8,Fof Community Value this restricts the
OL,9,Fability of the owner to dispose of it
OL,10,Fwithout first notifying Harborough
OL,11,FDistrict Council. Leicestershire
OL,12,FCounty Council owns the centre and has
OL,13,Fnotified the council of its intention
OL,14,Fto sell.
OL,16,F"The council has been helping charity
OL,17,FShopmobility, a tenant in the
OL,18,Fbuilding, find alternate suitable and
OL,19,Faffordable premises and we will
OL,20,Fcontinue to support where we can."
