OL,3,C'Nowhere to go': Charities facing
OL,4,Ceviction by council from the community
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"Tenants have been advised that the
OL,8,FCouncil was aiming for the 30th
OL,9,FOctober for the property to be
OL,10,Fvacated. In light of the timetable
OL,11,Fimposed by the asset of community
OL,12,Fvalue listing we are currently
OL,13,Fconsidering the position of all
OL,14,Fcurrent occupiers in terms of timing
OL,15,Faround vacating the property.
OL,17,F"We will continue to be in close
OL,18,Fdialogue to ensure they are kept fully
OL,19,Finformed."
